note: Nick Willis: Better known as Kaycin, is a music producer, sound designer, and mentor within FL Studios, with ambitions to grow into an audio software application developer. 10 years into his musical pursuit; He began helping others with music composition, such as basic music theory, midi arrangement, track structure, dynamics of a track, and overall fundamentals needed to start and finalize a production. "I soon realized I had a of passion for teaching, and potentially mentoring others"
